Everything indicates that the nightmares of the neighbors of House No. 51 on Balmes Street have ended.
Twelve people voluntarily left the building that they had illegally occupied and organized in which they had organised huge festivals that had driven the neighbourhood to despair. The room was held on a court order without police intervention.
